Q: How to run the game?
A:
1. You can directly run "./Tetris" to run the game.
2. To rereate the executable, you can run "make clean" first and then run "make".
   Then run "./Tetris" to run the game.

Q: Any steps not completed?
A: All steps and requirements are completed.

Q: Any additional features?
A:
1. When a new tile is dropping, it will show up row by row from the top of the game window.
2. Game will terminate if a new tile piece cannot be fit within the game window
   or it was stacked on the top row (makes the game a little tougher).
